Homepage: https://github.com/briankwest/libplcode
Description: Two-way radio signaling codec library — development files
 libplcode is a portable C99 library for encoding and decoding two-way radio
 signaling tones and codes in signed 16-bit linear PCM audio.
 .
 This package provides the header, static library, and pkg-config file
 needed to build applications against libplcode.
